<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en"><head><meta charset="utf-8"/><meta content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1" name="viewport"/><title>John Smith Guest Portal | Arbor Vista Retreat</title><meta content="noindex,nofollow,noarchive" name="robots"/><link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" rel="preconnect"/><link crossorigin="" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" rel="preconnect"/><link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:wght@500;600;700&amp;family=Manrope:wght@400;500;600;700;800&amp;display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/><link href="../../assets/style.css" rel="stylesheet"/></head><body class="home-page"><header class="nav"><div class="container navin"><a class="brand" href="../../index.html">Arbor Vista Retreat<small>Private guest portal · Demo</small></a><a class="btn outline" href="../../welcome.html">Public guide</a></div></header><main><section class="portal-hero"><div class="container"><div class="eyebrow" style="color:#f0c895">Your personalized stay</div><h1>Welcome, John!</h1><p class="hero-copy">Your Smoky Mountains getaway begins in <strong data-arrival="2026-08-15">24 days</strong>.</p><div class="snapshot"><div>Aug 15–19, 2026</div><div>4 adults · 2 children</div><div>2 bedrooms + loft</div><div>Reservation demo</div></div></div></section><section class="section soft"><div class="container"><div class="eyebrow">Stay progress</div><h2>Everything is moving along.</h2><div class="timeline"><div class="step done"><div class="step-icon">✓</div><div><h3>Booking confirmed</h3><p>Your reservation has been recorded.</p></div></div><div class="step done"><div class="step-icon">✓</div><div><h3>Rental agreement accepted</h3><p>Agreement status: complete.</p></div></div><div class="step" data-gate-pill=""><div class="step-icon">3</div><div><h3>Vehicle registration</h3><p data-gate-status="">Information needed</p></div></div><div class="step"><div class="step-icon">4</div><div><h3>Arrival information</h3><p>Available three days before check-in.</p></div></div></div></div></section><section class="section" id="gate-pass"><div class="container grid2" style="align-items:start"><div><div class="eyebrow">Shagbark gate pass</div><h2>Register your vehicle.</h2><p>Shagbark Resort requires guest vehicles to be registered before arrival. One vehicle is included; each additional vehicle is subject to a $10 resort fee.</p><div class="notice">For this test, only the driver’s name, email, phone and vehicle count are collected. No driver’s-license number or image is requested.</div></div><div class="form-shell"><div class="form-head"><h2 style="margin:0">Vehicle details</h2></div><form class="form-body form-grid" data-save="gate-pass-demo"><div class="field full"><label>Driver’s full name</label><input name="driver_name" required=""/></div><div class="field"><label>Email</label><input name="email" required="" type="email"/></div><div class="field"><label>Mobile phone</label><input name="phone" required="" type="tel"/></div><div class="field full"><label>Total vehicles</label><select name="vehicles"><option>1</option><option>2</option><option>3</option></select></div><div class="field full check"><input id="consent" required="" type="checkbox"/><label for="consent">I authorize Arbor Vista Retreat to share these details with Shagbark Resort for gate-pass processing.</label></div><div class="field full"><button class="btn gold">Submit vehicle details</button><div class="success" data-success="gate-pass-demo"><strong>Vehicle information received.</strong><br/>The portal status will update after refreshing this page.</div></div></form></div></div></section><section class="section dark"><div class="container"><div class="eyebrow" style="color:#f0c895">Arrival details</div><h2>Unlocked three days before check-in.</h2><div class="status-grid"><div class="status locked"><strong>Cabin address</strong>Available Aug 12</div><div class="status locked"><strong>Door code</strong>Last four digits of primary guest’s phone</div><div class="status locked"><strong>Wi-Fi &amp; parking</strong>Available Aug 12</div></div><p class="small" style="color:#c9d5d0;margin-top:18px">Static GitHub testing cannot automatically reveal these by date without placing the information in the page source. Production will use a secure backend later.</p></div></section><section class="section"><div class="container"><div class="eyebrow">Plan ahead</div><h2>Your guide is ready now.</h2><p><a class="btn primary" href="../../welcome.html">Open welcome guide</a> <a class="btn outline" href="../../rental-agreement.html">View agreement</a></p></div></section></main><script src="../../assets/script.js"></script></body></html>
